This project needs the CPAN SDL modules 

If you do not have these modules,
run the following commands in a shell :

perl -MCPAN -e 'install SDLx::App';
perl -MCPAN -e 'install SDL';
perl -MCPAN -e 'install SDL::Image';

To run the game :

perl src/Yonder.pl;


Graphics from opengameart.org and rpgrevolution.org, everything is Open Content


keyboard bindings:

 j -> scroll left
 i -> scroll up 
 k -> scroll down 
 l -> scroll right 
